{"tid":1843044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃離急症室武漢夫婦個女因無病徵當日**自行出院** 然後琴日發燒隔離","createTime":"2020-01-26T04:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T05:24:13.000Z","uid":71253,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"686734a68e2879efda9fcc07cac754fe27a51b50","tid":1843044,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n24號支那01：衞生防護中心傍晚透露，新增兩宗初步確診個案，其中一名是威院62歲女病人，其化驗結果對新型冠狀病毒呈初步陽性。據了解，其63歲丈夫同樣確診，兩人肺部影像「無花」。消息指兩人是內地人，從武漢來港，此行是探望居住在馬鞍山銀湖天峰的女兒，兩人被轉送瑪嘉烈隔離治療。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">據知其女兒昨晚無病徵，可自行出院</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一小時前蘋果：片段中沒有拍下及後情況，醫院職員最終報警求助，最終夫婦二人逃走失敗，由警員押送下返回醫院。兩人最終於當晚確診武漢肺炎，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其女兒為夫婦的密切接觸者，昨日亦因發燒而入院隔離。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n整理 <br />\n23號晚夫婦入院確診，個女離院<br />\n25號個女發燒入院<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公佈個女去左邊接觸過咩人未"},{"pid":"1db9d36cc54fe8f6fac33f3b0640ebc3a47533ea","tid":1843044,"uid":9104,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:44:57.000Z","msg":"屌 唔係十四日觀察既咩"},{"pid":"aaa4d7ded2653cc847b669a2a214802d1b5c5e76","tid":1843044,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"屌係咪on9"},{"pid":"085fc3f4ac9206f7c124c304e00fc450b35304c9","tid":1843044,"uid":71253,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1db9d36cc54fe8f6fac33f3b0640ebc3a47533ea","tid":1843044,"uid":9104,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:44:57.000Z","msg":"屌 唔係十四日觀察既咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"無病徵就走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" cla